{"tid":2452304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛病毒溯源專家團承認可能受到政治壓力 曾花大量精力咬文嚼字及中英翻譯","createTime":"2021-03-18T18:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T09:22:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"50400c164e2df6ecb811a09a6d100fc9abcca9f8","tid":2452304,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"世衛專家承認可能受到政治壓力<br />\n<br />\n早前到武漢進行新冠病毒溯源工作的世衛專家組組長安巴雷克承認，小組成員可能受到政治壓力，但保證報告內容獲得成員一致支持。他說，全長280頁的報告會在下星期發表，內容包括圖表、數據及附錄。安巴雷克表示，報告由所有專家撰寫，形容過程複雜而漫長。他們曾集中微調科學議題上的文本內容，並花了大量時間進行中英文翻譯。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2383623&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=e38ed235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383623</a>"},{"pid":"3ca38085b7ae881c70b5fd4cdc3ca8389ba076a1","tid":2452304,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T18:10:37.000Z","msg":"可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c8bbb47566fd40a97e66c26fecb6df51164523","tid":2452304,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac888391d5ca1ed9f1f6104bb805137092e80677","tid":2452304,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"又話根據科學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142d0f14e498cab553e7bce281e0d980c78b16d4","tid":2452304,"uid":189453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"份野有可能有問題 但又一致同意 咁到底有無問題 科學嘅野可以咁撚樣求其？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78444a44790869bcb672741ae0006145c6a5e4a","tid":